title: Love.Stinks[1999][DvDrip][Eng]-Criptkprr
description: Hollywood sitcom writer Seth Winnick (French Stewart) meets gorgeous Chelsea Turner (Bridgette Wilson) at a wedding, and they begin a hot-and-heavy relationship. Soon Turner becomes ruthless in her efforts to force a marriage Winnick doesn't want, and an all-out battle of the sexes ensues as their passion turns to malice. This unhappily-ever-after comedy features cameos by Jason Bateman, Christian Slater and Tiffani-Amber Thiessen.
